{"type": "article", "id": 7898, "title": "Norden 香氛蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-30T07:42:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234903Zi78Sawb0IN9tzAp.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t香氛蜡烛目前正在慢慢成为许多人生活的必不可少的部分，Norden 公司最近推出了一系列新调味的香氛蜡烛，蜡烛底座采用陶瓷材质，简洁大方，香味是香草/甜橙、松香/柑橘，雪松/鼠尾草三种可选，燃烧时长为 80 小时。蜡烛烧完后，陶瓷容器可以洗净重复利用。目前售价为 45 美元，<a href=\"http://www.nordengoods.com/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349017uL4w6b0tfyWCqrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234901y5nKzew0uVXCBxE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234902WpNsGd4thwPAaHUz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}